{"tid":1466404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［不分化！不割席！］希望大家可以停止捉鬼","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T21:49:34.000Z","uid":25640,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"977f26688d45323e23c01cbe42182ba10a8cd772","tid":1466404,"uid":25640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:42:48.000Z","msg":"大家抱住捉鬼心態真係好影響個運動<br />\n因為大家會對手足唔信任<br />\n覺得佢勇啲就係鬼！<br />\n希望大家可以對手足多啲信任<br />\n唔好成日諗住捉鬼 好似2014年咁<br />\n諗下點贏好過 贏會完 捉鬼唔會完<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住不分化！不割席！不捉鬼！</span></span>"},{"pid":"24dc6a3c57b569eb571eca889f9fbff865fcf040","tid":1466404,"uid":25640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:44:36.000Z","msg":"自推十野"},{"pid":"d31126a0fd690543e4b2ca783d2c5e1a12eaca5f","tid":1466404,"uid":25640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:44:54.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"019b7c3c3ca50069150bd4f104aacab4d8ce571e","tid":1466404,"uid":25640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:08.000Z","msg":"二"},{"pid":"e0f444685c38f01ab4c68f8d4d2590c9f56ea879","tid":1466404,"uid":43510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:09.000Z","msg":"不分化不割席<br />\n<br />\n但係咪連見到捉鬼既人都不割席"},{"pid":"486ddcd85c75ab201d79d31e05d6b8fda04023cb","tid":1466404,"uid":25640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e0f444685c38f01ab4c68f8d4d2590c9f56ea879","tid":1466404,"uid":43510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:09.000Z","msg":"不分化不割席<br />\n<br />\n但係咪連見到捉鬼既人都不割席"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:48:02.000Z","msg":"唔割席但善意提醒<br />\n知道捉鬼既人都係想場運動好<br />\n但捉鬼依種心態好容易成為左割席既種子<br />\n好希望唔捉鬼依個思想可以成為主流"},{"pid":"c89dd0407b0949c44619b75eaacad8827a6737fc","tid":1466404,"uid":25640,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:48:13.000Z","msg":"三"},{"pid":"976bea5a00eb17a3eea781b3f891864f075d6bee","